# elx : enterprise linux base image by xtalcloud

# changes: v0.3-rc2
- tmux upgrade to 3.2, syntax of tmux.conf changed
- zsh echoing CTRL sequences has been fixed
- shellcheck was added
- added z to work with nnn

# changes: v0.3-rc3
- zsh/tmux integration


# changes: v0.3-rc5
- entire project has ben rewritten in HCL, still working out the kinks

# changes: v0.4
- added Rocky Linux 10 support (http/el10/ks.cfg, rocky10.pkrvars.hcl)
- build now defaults to the current Rocky Linux 10 release
- template parameterized via variables.pkr.hcl (iso, version, arch, credentials)
- iso_checksum tracks Rocky's published CHECKSUM file (works across point releases)
- kickstart now creates the 'ansible' build user with passwordless sudo;
  provisioners run via sudo
- htop added to the standard tool set
- rg and htop now install from EPEL so they work on both EL9 and EL10

